loads/2025/02/adobe-online-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-levels.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adobe-online-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-levels.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2080\" height=\"1170\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Adobe online PDF compressor tool showing different compression levels\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adobe-online-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-levels.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adobe-online-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-levels.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Adobe\u0026#39;s online PDF compressor is another reliable option, especially if you\u0026#39;re already invested in the Adobe ecosystem. While it\u0026#39;s limited to processing one file at a time for free, it makes up for this with a clean, user-friendly interface that previews your estimated file size before compressing.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWhen you upload a PDF, Adobe\u0026#39;s tool predicts the compressed file size for each of its three quality settings:\u003c/p\u003e        \u003cul\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        \u003cstrong\u003eHigh\u003c/strong\u003e for maximum compression\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        \u003cstrong\u003eMedium\u003c/strong\u003e for a balance of size and quality\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        \u003cstrong\u003eLow\u003c/strong\u003e for the highest quality output.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis feature comes in handy since \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/this-is-the-best-browser-pdf-reader/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emost browsers have built-in PDF readers\u003c/a\u003e these days.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eOne thing to keep in mind is that Adobe\u0026#39;s servers handle your files during the compression process. Adobe states that these files are securely deleted after processing unless you\u0026#39;re signed in and choose to save them to your Adobe account.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_16\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003eIf you need to compress multiple PDFs at once, you\u0026#39;ll have to step up to Adobe Acrobat Pro. While not free, Acrobat Pro offers batch compression and other powerful PDF editing features that make it worth the price for heavy users.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"pdf2go\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://www.pdf2go.com/compress-pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePDF2Go\u003c/a\u003e\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdf2go-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-options.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdf2go-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-options.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdf2go-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-options.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdf2go-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-options.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdf2go-pdf-compressor-tool-showing-different-compression-options.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                               